DataElement.preferredName: Other Related Hemoglobin Allele Sickle Cell Disease Type Level Percentage Value
DataElement.preferredDefinition: The numeric laboratory percentage value measured, assigned or computed related to the level of the other related sickle cell disease hemoglobin allele.
